sentences.english: Follow these steps to download, unzip and install to TRAINZ .
sentences.chinese: 按下列步骤下载，解压缩后完整装入TRAINZ。

sentences.english: The files are automatically decompressed after being downloaded.
sentences.chinese: 文件在下载完成之后会自动解压缩。

sentences.english: Extract that file to your plugins directory, as well.
sentences.chinese: 将该文件也解压缩到插件目录中。

sentences.english: Specifically, download the source code archive and extract it to a directory of your choice.

sentences.english: Installation only takes unzipping an archive.
sentences.chinese: 安装只需要解压缩的存档。

sentences.english: Occasionally, you'll run into a downloaded file which needs to be decompressed or un-zipped before installation.
sentences.chinese: 有时候，你会碰到需要在安装前先解压缩的下载文件。

sentences.english: Once you have downloaded this file, extract its contents.
sentences.chinese: 下载这个文件之后，对其进行解压缩。

sentences.chinese: 我最近写的一个LZW的压缩与解压缩程序。
